Class jsonObject

java.lang.Object
jsonElement
jsonComplexElement
jsonObject
public class jsonObject extends jsonComplexElement
jsonObject is used to hold information for json object elements. The class is required because of the objectContext ctx. The jsonComplexElement parent class allows both arrays and objects to make use of the same methods but be instantiated with the correct ctx type.
